## Design Considerations

### ESC Key Priority System
- Higher z-index = Higher priority
- Modal (z-50) > AITerminal (z-40) > Base (z-0)
- First handler calls `stopPropagation()` to prevent bubbling
- Capture phase ensures topmost handler runs first

### AI Terminal Button Placement
- Top-right matches close button location
- 50% smaller (w-10 h-10 vs w-14 h-14)
- `mr-2 mt-2` provides spacing from edge (user preference)
- Hidden when terminal open (conditional rendering)

### WeatherMap Padding
- Consistent p-4 padding on map and forecast sections
- Aligns with design system spacing
- Prevents harsh edge-to-border contact
- Better readability and visual hierarchy

### Theme-Aware Tooltips
- Use semantic color tokens (surface-light-elevated, text-light-primary)
- Automatically adjust for light/dark mode
- Maintains contrast ratios (WCAG AA)

